Enable or disable preferring ducksf replacements over sf (no attach)

sf_use_ducksf.Rd

Since ducksf does not export any functions with the same names as sf, there is nothing to prefer/mask at runtime. This helper is kept only for backward compatibility and will just inform the user.

Usage

sf_use_ducksf(use = NULL, allow = NULL, deny = NULL, silent = FALSE)

Arguments

use

Ignored (kept for compatibility).

allow

Ignored.

deny

Ignored.

silent

Logical; if TRUE, suppress messages.

Value

Invisibly returns character(0).
